How CashKaro Works

What is CashKaro Cashback?

When you visit any online site, such as Amazon or Myntra, by clicking through CashKaro and make a purchase, we receive a marketing fee. We then pass on most of this fee to you in the form of 'Cashback'. Easily earn Up to ₹20,000 in Cashback with just 1 extra click

3 Steps to Earn up to ₹20,000 per year

  • Login to CashKaro & click on any of our retailers or deal of your choice.. Eg. Amazon, Myntra, Flash Deals, Finance Etc.
  • You will be redirected to the retailer’s site. Shop as you normally do
  • Get Instant discounts with Promo Codes + Up to 70% Cashback. Transfer Cashback directly to your bank account.

Up to 75% Savings via our Best Coupons & Cashback

Save double with our Best Deals and Cashback on Amazon, Apple, Nykaa etc.

You can also earn rewards on credit card applications on SBI, HDFC & Axis Bank.

Transfer Cashback to your Bank Account or as Gift Cards

Cashback earned on Amazon, Myntra, Nykaa can be transferred to your Bank Account as Real Cash or as Amazon / Flipkart Gift Cards.

Our Cashback is on top of discounts and all credit card cashback deals!
